For complete installation of the app, login as admin and run these paths

## Create locations
/endpoint?action_model=15&action_id=update

## Create product categories
/endpoint?action_model=17&action_id=update

## Create UOMS
/endpoint?action_model=19&action_id=update_unit
/endpoint?action_model=19&action_id=update_currency



## Note, it will only create 100 records for locations and product categories if the application is not in development mode

